text: To sum this up, I'm excited about the work we've done and continue to be doing in this space. It's interesting and lies on a unique intersection of exciting engineering challenges and dramatic usage scale, with a wide gamut of experience for language users.

We have limited resources as well; it would be nice to invest more time into extra tools (formatter, LSP) but core language improvements require our entire attention right now.

This is an area where community involvement could also help significantly accelerate progress.

This was an open-source release, not a code drop. We sync this repository with our internal copy every week, and we release every week. We're up to release #25 since we've open sourced!

We've also merged a number of patches from the community, both inside and outside of Roblox.
